4
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:41,460
You are way better than his son,

5
00:01:42,140 --> 00:01:43,060
but his son is better

6
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:44,539
at buttering people up.

7
00:01:44,660 --> 00:01:45,660
You know he's not as good as me,

8
00:01:46,580 --> 00:01:47,460
but Mum still arranged Qin

9
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:48,500
to go on a blind date with him.

10
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,440
He's not as capable as you,

11
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:51,860
but he's not a bad person.

12
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:54,490
If we have to find her someone as good as you,

13
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:56,450
[Erudite and discerning]

14
00:01:54,780 --> 00:01:56,180
how many men in Yancheng can qualify?

15
00:01:56,509 --> 00:01:57,270
If we just keep on looking,

16
00:01:57,300 --> 00:01:58,380
how can your sister

17
00:01:58,820 --> 00:01:59,820
get married?

18
00:02:00,510 --> 00:02:01,620
It's okay if she doesn't.

19
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:02,990
It's not like we can't provide for her.

20
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,000
What are you even talking about?

21
00:02:07,290 --> 00:02:08,460
I really can't understand

22
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:09,699
young people like you nowadays.

23
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:12,440
Uncle Gu's daughter is great.

24
00:02:13,070 --> 00:02:14,510
But you don't like her either.

25
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,380
What have you been up to lately?

26
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,560
Why haven't you come home on weekends?

27
00:02:25,490 --> 00:02:26,680
It's almost the end of the year.

28
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:28,680
I'm a little busy.

29
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:29,980
So is Qin.

30
00:02:30,340 --> 00:02:31,579
She hasn't been home

31
00:02:31,690 --> 00:02:32,579
since she came back from the disaster area.

32
00:02:32,690 --> 00:02:34,000
Every time I called her,

33
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:34,910
she said she was busy.

34
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:36,820
I don't know what you're busy with.

35
00:02:39,410 --> 00:02:40,670
She didn't come home last weekend either?

36
00:02:40,790 --> 00:02:41,670
No.

37
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:56,730
Dr. Xu, we're leaving.

38
00:02:56,730 --> 00:02:57,540
Bye.

39
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:02,980
Are you off work?

40
00:03:03,250 --> 00:03:04,060
I'm on my way.

41
00:03:09,370 --> 00:03:10,320
It'll be a bit late today.

42
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:11,700
I'll leave in ten minutes.

43
00:03:14,950 --> 00:03:15,420
Okay.

