49
00:04:19,450 --> 00:04:20,050
Brother.

50
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:33,150
Go up.

51
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:36,159
Come home with me.

52
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,060
Meng Yanchen.

53
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:50,550
You are her brother.

54
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:57,200
You two can't be together.

55
00:05:05,850 --> 00:05:07,130
As long as our parents don't agree,

56
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,720
you two can't get married.

57
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:12,080
Since you got together,

58
00:05:12,510 --> 00:05:13,790
she's never come home.

59
00:05:14,250 --> 00:05:15,360
She's just avoiding the problem.

60
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:17,840
Don't you understand?

61
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:23,880
Don't you worry about it.

62
00:05:24,420 --> 00:05:25,500
Whether I can keep her or not

63
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,560
depends on how good I am.

64
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:28,680
Right.

65
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:30,100
Keep her.

66
00:05:31,150 --> 00:05:31,950
Then what?

67
00:05:32,450 --> 00:05:33,970
Asking her to give up everything for you

68
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:36,560
just to satisfy your own desire?

69
00:05:37,330 --> 00:05:38,659
Will you be at ease?

70
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,560
Song Yan.

71
00:05:41,620 --> 00:05:42,690
Ask yourself.

72
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,409
Do you deserve her?

73
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:20,590
Check out the environment of this neighborhood.

74
00:06:21,390 --> 00:06:22,470
Weigh yourself.

75
00:06:23,540 --> 00:06:24,820
Can't you see clearly?

76
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:27,910
You were dumped back then

77
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,560
because our parents didn't approve.

78
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,800
If you still have any

79
00:06:31,850 --> 00:06:32,960
dignity and guts,

80
00:06:33,150 --> 00:06:34,230
you'd do anything you can

81
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:35,159
to make yourself

82
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:35,920
presentable

83
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,240
so that you can deserve her.

84
00:06:37,710 --> 00:06:38,860
But look at yourself.

85
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,450
What do you have?

86
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:41,840
What can you give her?

87
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:43,870
Asking her to stand on the opposite side

88
00:06:44,730 --> 00:06:46,570
of everything she has just for you?

89
00:06:48,490 --> 00:06:49,530
Song Yan.

90
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,760
Who do you think you are?

91
00:07:03,700 --> 00:07:04,700
Meng Yanchen.

92
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:07,630
Do you know her?

93
00:07:10,730 --> 00:07:12,570
Besides knowing that she is sensitive

94
00:07:12,790 --> 00:07:14,120
and dull,

95
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,130
what else do you know?

96
00:07:20,650 --> 00:07:22,810
You don't know her at all.

97
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:24,940
Yes.

98
00:07:25,860 --> 00:07:27,420
You've hated me since ten years ago.

99
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:29,660
You hated me for teaching her to smoke,

100
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:30,760
drink,

101
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:31,910
and fight.

102
00:07:32,909 --> 00:07:33,840
But what really happened?

103
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:36,700
She was the one

104
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:38,520
who asked me to take her to a bar.

105
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,880
I don't fight.

106
00:07:40,450 --> 00:07:42,000
She just picked fights with others herself.

107
00:07:43,620 --> 00:07:44,780
Do you know why?

108
00:07:47,460 --> 00:07:48,530
She wanted to play.

109
00:07:49,210 --> 00:07:50,170
She wanted to act wildly.

110
00:07:50,530 --> 00:07:51,570
She wanted to go crazy.

111
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,960
She wanted freedom.

112
00:07:54,290 --> 00:07:55,610
She had been suppressed for too long,

113
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:57,820
so the way she did it was extreme.

114
00:08:01,530 --> 00:08:02,540
At that time,

115
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:05,910
at least she was vivid.

116
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,550
So,

117
00:08:12,340 --> 00:08:13,650
you ask me why I deserve her?

118
00:08:17,900 --> 00:08:19,620
Just for her laughter just now.

119
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,760
At least she was full of life back then.

120
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:24,960
What about now?

121
00:08:26,530 --> 00:08:27,900
Ten years have passed,

122
00:08:28,780 --> 00:08:30,500
and she's been suppressed to be completely numb.

123
00:08:31,090 --> 00:08:32,809
Don't you know her personality?

124
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,400
She seems cold

125
00:08:36,020 --> 00:08:37,380
and unconcerned about anything on the outside.

126
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:39,760
But in fact,

127
00:08:40,650 --> 00:08:41,850
she's just a coward.

128
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,480
No matter how well she disguises herself,

129
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,970
she's just a pushover.

130
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:47,120
Even if she's suppressed to death,

131
00:08:48,130 --> 00:08:49,850
she wouldn't say a word of complaint to you.

132
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:52,120
She treats you as her next of kin.

133
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:55,300
But what do you take her for?

134
00:08:58,020 --> 00:08:59,460
You treat her as a pawn,

135
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,000
making her marry for business

136
00:09:01,430 --> 00:09:02,520
to pave the way

137
00:09:02,550 --> 00:09:03,460
for your family enterprise?

138
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,720
I won't use her to pave the way.

139
00:09:05,740 --> 00:09:06,980
Can you protect her?

140
00:09:08,530 --> 00:09:10,010
You can't even protect yourself.

141
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:11,670
Meng Yanchen.

142
00:09:18,980 --> 00:09:19,970
My parents

143
00:09:21,370 --> 00:09:23,070
are not as bad as you said.

144
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,030
They do have

145
00:09:24,050 --> 00:09:25,130
their own set of

146
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:25,880
rules.

147
00:09:26,530 --> 00:09:28,170
This set of rules does suppress me

148
00:09:28,430 --> 00:09:29,580
and Qin.

149
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:30,710
But...

150
00:09:30,990 --> 00:09:32,510
Qin is her daughter.

151
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,240
They treat her as their own daughter.

152
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:37,450
Meng Yanchen.

153
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:38,780
You know very well

154
00:09:39,930 --> 00:09:41,370
she's not only Meng Qin,

155
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:44,000
but also Xu Qin.

156
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:49,940
Go back.

157
00:09:51,070 --> 00:09:52,110
You and your family.

158
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,160
Please don't make things difficult for her anymore.

159
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:13,470
She has had insomnia for a long time.

160
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:17,000
She needs sleeping pills to fall asleep.

161
00:10:17,350 --> 00:10:18,120
Do you know that?

162
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:21,400
You said this neighborhood is good.

163
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:23,800
It really is.

164
00:10:25,870 --> 00:10:27,150
The floor is good too.

165
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:29,480
It's very high.

166
00:10:31,170 --> 00:10:32,170
Meng Yanchen.

167
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:34,870
Look up.

168
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:38,200
Given her previous state,

169
00:10:40,210 --> 00:10:41,410
do you think one day,

170
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,560
she'd jump

171
00:10:47,230 --> 00:10:48,220
from above?

172
00:11:02,060 --> 00:11:03,100
None of your family

173
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:05,180
has the right

174
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:08,300
to say I don't deserve her.

175
00:11:31,460 --> 00:11:32,660
You two didn't fight, did you?

176
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,240
Go.

177
00:11:36,740 --> 00:11:37,710
Check downstairs.

178
00:12:53,740 --> 00:12:54,670
What's wrong with you recently?

179
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,200
Nothing.

180
00:12:57,190 --> 00:12:58,230
Do you think I believe you?

181
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:03,700
What do you want me to say?

182
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:14,040
This is not how you should drink wine.

183
00:13:14,950 --> 00:13:16,230
Wine is supposed to be tasted,

184
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:18,110
and bring happiness to people.

185
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:19,750
It's not for drinking your problems away.

186
00:13:20,430 --> 00:13:21,550
Who is it this time?

187
00:13:22,140 --> 00:13:23,380
It has nothing to do with others.

188
00:13:25,340 --> 00:13:26,460
I just want to drink.

189
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,430
Seriously?

190
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:30,860
Torture yourself like this?

191
00:13:33,820 --> 00:13:34,860
There are two caterpillars

192
00:13:37,060 --> 00:13:38,710
living in a dark cave.

193
00:13:40,410 --> 00:13:41,650
There's no light.

194
00:13:42,750 --> 00:13:43,790
It's very depressing.

195
00:13:46,550 --> 00:13:47,910
They're just caterpillars.

196
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,720
Neither of them can escape.

197
00:13:52,950 --> 00:13:54,350
But luckily, there are two of them.

198
00:13:56,020 --> 00:13:57,580
They can depend on each other.

199
00:14:02,190 --> 00:14:03,310
Although it's dark,

200
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:05,760
they have each other's company.

201
00:14:06,910 --> 00:14:08,350
But one day,

202
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,840
one of them comes out of the cocoon,

203
00:14:14,490 --> 00:14:15,930
turns into a butterfly, and flies away.

204
00:14:17,250 --> 00:14:18,680
The other caterpillar

205
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:22,150
is still in the cave.

206
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,150
Still in the endless darkness.

207
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:28,740
The other caterpillar

208
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:30,440
will turn into a butterfly too.

209
00:14:31,430 --> 00:14:33,110
There are too many butterflies outside.

210
00:14:36,270 --> 00:14:37,350
No matter how hard it searches,

211
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:41,800
it can't find

212
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,990
that caterpillar from before.

213
00:14:48,430 --> 00:14:49,740
You two used to

214
00:14:49,740 --> 00:14:51,390
bear the suppression of your mum together.

215
00:14:51,830 --> 00:14:52,590
Now, Qin

216
00:14:52,590 --> 00:14:54,180
is pursuing her own happiness.

217
00:14:54,980 --> 00:14:56,740
The pressure she and Song Yan will face

218
00:14:56,780 --> 00:14:58,530
will only be 1,000 times greater than you.

219
00:14:58,930 --> 00:15:00,090
In comparison,

220
00:15:00,390 --> 00:15:01,910
they are braver than you.

221
00:15:02,740 --> 00:15:03,690
No matter what,

222
00:15:04,710 --> 00:15:05,910
as long as they fly out,

223
00:15:06,450 --> 00:15:07,930
there'll be a vast world out there.

224
00:15:08,770 --> 00:15:09,800
It's obviously better than

225
00:15:09,830 --> 00:15:10,990
staying in the dark forever.

226
00:15:24,010 --> 00:15:25,690
He's always a decent man.

227
00:15:26,290 --> 00:15:27,260
I'm also surprised

228
00:15:27,530 --> 00:15:28,490
about today.

229
00:15:29,990 --> 00:15:30,940
I know.

230
00:15:31,780 --> 00:15:32,950
I knew it long ago.

231
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:35,670
What do you know?

232
00:15:37,500 --> 00:15:38,900
I know it's not been easy

233
00:15:39,470 --> 00:15:40,220
for you to be in that family.

234
00:15:40,550 --> 00:15:41,900
It's not about how difficult it is.

235
00:15:42,940 --> 00:15:44,070
It's just that when we are with family,

236
00:15:44,620 --> 00:15:45,350
it's not that easy

237
00:15:45,350 --> 00:15:46,500
to tell

238
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:47,580
who's right and who's wrong.

239
00:15:49,230 --> 00:15:50,910
You think my mum is tough, right?

240
00:15:52,340 --> 00:15:53,140
Indeed.

241
00:15:54,390 --> 00:15:55,740
She's very controlling.

242
00:15:57,350 --> 00:15:58,470
But you know what?

243
00:15:58,990 --> 00:15:59,940
When I had a fever

244
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:01,390
in my childhood,

245
00:16:01,830 --> 00:16:03,180
she was the one

246
00:16:03,650 --> 00:16:04,490
who kept me company all night.

247
00:16:06,570 --> 00:16:08,050
When someone bullied me,

248
00:16:08,740 --> 00:16:10,300
she was also the one who stood up for me.

249
00:16:11,120 --> 00:16:12,280
Surprised?

250
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:17,430
It's just my mum's personality is like that.

251
00:16:17,570 --> 00:16:18,670
She treats Meng Yanchen

252
00:16:18,940 --> 00:16:20,030
and me in the same way.

253
00:16:22,370 --> 00:16:24,330
My brother is very much like me.

254
00:16:26,430 --> 00:16:28,230
We are like caterpillars.

255
00:16:29,140 --> 00:16:30,860
We spinned ourselves in a cocoon,

256
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:34,000
thinking that we were hiding in a safe zone.

257
00:16:37,330 --> 00:16:38,490
Once anything

258
00:16:38,520 --> 00:16:40,030
changes in this zone,

259
00:16:40,790 --> 00:16:42,630
we'd suddenly lose our sense of security.

260
00:16:44,660 --> 00:16:46,220
My brother thinks

261
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:48,560
the other caterpillar ran away.

262
00:16:49,030 --> 00:16:50,150
He has no companion now,

263
00:16:51,020 --> 00:16:52,230
and he's abandoned.

264
00:16:54,710 --> 00:16:56,190
That's why he feels uneasy.

265
00:17:04,260 --> 00:17:05,579
From now on, your safe zone

266
00:17:07,020 --> 00:17:07,790
will be me.

267
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:27,599
Warm water.

268
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:30,210
Where is the wine?

269
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:32,680
The wine was the boss's.

270
00:17:33,140 --> 00:17:33,980
I'll buy one bottle.

271
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:37,490
What do you want?

272
00:17:37,550 --> 00:17:38,350
Anything.

273
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:39,920
Okay.

274
00:17:47,150 --> 00:17:48,270
I'm in the bar.

275
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,200
Okay, got it.

276
00:17:50,230 --> 00:17:50,670
Okay.

277
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:52,140
Wait a minute.

278
00:17:52,850 --> 00:17:54,210
Okay, I'll be right back.

279
00:17:55,190 --> 00:17:56,110
Who is the wine for?

280
00:17:56,130 --> 00:17:56,770
Mr. Meng.

281
00:17:57,670 --> 00:17:58,830
Who allowed you to open the wine for him?

282
00:17:59,100 --> 00:17:59,870
He paid the bill.

283
00:17:59,890 --> 00:18:00,760
Why can't I open it?

284
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:03,270
Will you be responsible if he gets drunk?

285
00:18:03,830 --> 00:18:04,470
Yes.

286
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:08,550
Yes?

287
00:18:11,350 --> 00:18:12,270
Ye'zi.

288
00:18:13,690 --> 00:18:15,330
I remember you are from a pretty good college.

289
00:18:15,750 --> 00:18:17,110
It's already graduation season.

290
00:18:17,140 --> 00:18:18,540
Why haven't you been looking for a proper job

291
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:19,720
